-- Hugo Boss Plans to Hire Hundreds by 2015, Stuttgarter Reports
-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 2012-02-18T10:37:50Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-18/hugo-boss-plans-to-hire-hundreds-by-2015-stuttgarter-reports.html
Hugo Boss AG (BOS)  plans to employ 100 to
200 workers a year by 2015,  Stuttgarter Nachrichten  reported,
citing an interview with Chief Executive Officer Claus-Dietrich Lahrs.  The jobs will be created “in Metzingen and around,” the
newspaper cited Lahrs as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Julie Cruz in Frankfurt at 
